        "description": {
            "value": "<p>A mesmerizing gemstone caps the head of this handsomely crafted wooden staff. While wielding the staff, you gain a +2 circumstance bonus to checks to identify enchantment magic.</p>\n<p><strong>Activate</strong> Cast a Spell</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> You expend a number of charges from the staff to cast a spell from its list.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Cantrip</strong> <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Daze]</em></li>\n<li><strong>1st</strong> <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Charm]</em>, <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Command]</em></li>\n<li><strong>2nd</strong> <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Hideous Laughter]</em>, <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Touch of Idiocy]</em></li>\n<li><strong>3rd</strong> <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Paralyze]</em></li>\n<li><strong>4th</strong> <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Charm]</em>, <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Confusion]</em>, <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Suggestion]</em></li>\n<li><strong>5th</strong> <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Command]</em>, <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Crushing Despair]</em></li>\n<li><strong>6th</strong> <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Dominate]</em>, <em>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Feeblemind]</em></li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Craft Requirements</strong> Supply one casting of all listed levels of all listed spells.</p>"
